usage: statreport.py [-h] [-m] [-p] [-c CONFIG]

Generate miner status report.

optional arguments:
  -h, --help            show this help message and exit
  -m, --email           send email
  -p, --plot            plot hash speed graph
  -c CONFIG, --config CONFIG
                        use another config file rather than ./statreport.conf                        
                        
in crontab:
# m h  dom mon dow   command
0 1-23/2 * * * cd ~/path/to/statreport;./statreport.py
0      0 * * * cd ~/path/to/statreport;./statreport.py -m
0      2 * * * cd ~/path/to/statreport;./statreport.py -mp
0 4-22/2 * * * cd ~/path/to/statreport;./statreport.py -m
